## 🏗️ Tech Stack

- **Frontend**: React + Tailwind + Chart.js
- **Backend**: Python (FastAPI)  
- **Database**: PostgreSQL  
- **Integrations**: Fireblocks API (mocked), Lark Bot, Telegram Bot API  
- **Hosting**: Render / Vercel / On-prem (TBD)

